org.openstreetmap.josm.plugins.streetside

Class StreetsideAbstractImage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openstreetmap.josm.plugins.streetside.StreetsideAbstractImage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<StreetsideAbstractImage>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StreetsideCubemap, StreetsideImage, StreetsideImportedImage

    public abstract class StreetsideAbstractImage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<StreetsideAbstractImage>
    Abstract superclass for all image objects. At the moment there are 3, StreetsideImportedImage, StreetsideImage, & StreetsideCubemap.
